cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause encryption negotiation failure during the security setup phase and prevent secure communication establishment.

du.explanation_en: Setting max MIMO layers to 0 disables MIMO functionality entirely, which may lead to degraded signal quality and connection instability in multi-antenna scenarios.
du.explanation_zh: 將最大 MIMO 層數設定為 0 會完全禁用 MIMO 功能，這可能導致多天線場景中的信號品質下降和連接不穩定。
